description:
imaedia hat sich nun auf vier Kernbereiche festgelegt. Digital Lifestyle, Technik, Unterhaltung und Apple. Diese Themen liegen mir auch sehr am Herzen da ich täglich mit ihnen umgehe. Der Alltag wird zunehmend technischer und die Produktvielfalt komplexer. Kaum jemand kann mehr den Markt überblicken. Ich versuche hier gezielt Produkte vorzustellen, von denen ich denke, dass sie von hohem Nutzwert und Qualität sind. Sicherlich werde ich hier und da auch mal Abschweifen und Negativbeispiele für schlechte Produkte und Produkte für den Spezialeinsatz vorstellen. Auch habe ich mir vorbehalten einen Bereich Off-Topic einzurichten, in dem alles landet, was gesagt werden muss, aber nicht konkret mit dem Thema zu tun hat. 
Impressum: http://www.imaedia.de/impressum/

description:
When I was a young boy (1950's), I learned to play golf by closely watching the best players at the course I grew up on. I would then stand in front of a window and copy their swings... then I would go to the practice area to ingrain that look and new feeling to muscle memory. That WAS and STILL IS a great way to learn! It's called SELF-DISCOVERY! 

When you discover a helpful motion or thought ALL BY YOURSELF, YOU WILL NEVER FORGET IT! - I never have!  

At the age of 78, I'm still a mid single-digit player. My goal with this YouTube channel is to provide a platform for TEACHING and LEARNING! I will provide videos and detailed descriptions of the finest golfers in the world, their swings and some of their finest shots so YOU can learn and improve as I have. 

The focus here is geared toward TEACHING and LEARNING the short game (putting, chipping, pitching and wedge play from 120-yards in), but you will also see some of the finest, Tour-Proven full swings and descriptions as well.⛳️

description:
A bath of silicon oil is vibrated and oil droplets are deposited on the surface. Thanks to the vibrations, the droplets do not coalesce, but bounce on the surface.

For specific values of amplitude and frequencies, the droplet start to move forward by itself : while bouncing, it create waves with which it interacts.

This object has been called a walker, and exhibits properties reminiscent of an elementary particle, because it is at the same time a particle (the droplet) and a wave (The local standing wave pattern created by the droplet)

description:
Špičková hydromasážní sprcha Alexejeva je unikátní technický vynález. Pomocí masážní sprchy můžete provádět celou řadu hydromasážních procedur.

Připravili jsme pro Vás video kanál, na kterém si můžete funkčnost masážní sprchy Alexejeva ověřit. Náš kanál také obsahuje slow motion videa natočená rychlostí až 60 000 snímků za vteřinu. Z nich je patrné, jak unikátní je technické řešení použité při vývoji sprchy Alexejeva.

Hydromasáž je vysoce účinná léčebná metoda, která Vám pomůže zbavit se řady zdravotních problémů. Pomáhá například při léčbě bolesti zápěstí, celulitidy, křečových žil a také při regeneraci celého těla.

Pomocí masážní sprchy Alexejeva lze také provádět lymfodrenáž v pohodlí Vašeho domova.

I played USTA juniors growing up competing at the Georgia, Southern and National Level. I went on to play two years of college tennis and then transferred to finish my major at another institution.  Immediately following graduation, I started training and played 4 years of competitive professional tennis (ITF Futures, USTA procircuit and Men's Open events in the United States).

I took this experience to assistant coaching at the college level.  Within a couple years I attained a Head Coach position for M/W Teams.  None of this would have been possible without support from family, wife, friends, coaches, training mates and many more along the path.  

This channel is to help get the message out about key concepts that simplify the game of tennis.  Strokes, drills, nutrtional advice, etc will all be explained with their core fundamentals and values for every level to comprehend and implement.

Thank you and happy hitting!!!

* Improve your golf swing so you can continue to play even as you age

 Me encanta ser un friki en informática, buscar agujeros por donde colarse en un sistema y sacarle ese plus que nos han quitado o no han pensado los fabricantes de tecnología. Disfruto cacharreando con Linux, Macs, Raspberry Pi, Arduino para hacer inventos que luego no tengo tiempo de publicar ;-)

Como no podía ser de otra forma, soy un fanático del motor, me encantan los audi, y disfruto conduciendo el mio en circuito cada vez que puedo.

Espero poder ir subiendo videos de lo que voy cacharreando. Actualmente dedico mucho tiempo al retrofitado de funcionalidades nuevas en Audi. También a la seguridad informática de los sistemas que montan, los MMI 3G en linux.

Herzlich Willkommen auf meinem Kanal !
ich lebe in Deutschland ( Bayern ) und beschäftige mich mit dem Thema Video/Foto schon seit einiger Zeit. Meine aktuellen Kameras sind die Panasonic Lumix GX 80, Lumix G70, Lumix G5, die neue DJI OSMO Pocket 3, Yi 4K Plus (Actioncam) die GOPRO HERO 8 BLACK (Actioncam) und die neue Insta360 X4 (360 Grad Kamera). Für Luftaufnahmen kommt seit Anfang April 2023 die DJI Air 2s und die dafür passende fliegende 360 Grad Kamera Insta360 Sphere zum Einsatz. Ich filme heute fast nur noch in 4K. Die Filmthemen die mich interessieren sind sehr breitgefächert, dass sind sowohl Reisefilme ( weltweit ), Filme von Motorsportveranstaltungen aber auch alles andere Interessante. description:
My YouTube Philosophy- 

I love making YouTube videos because I love creating content. Making videos is a form of art to me, and putting them out in the world for anyone to see is a passion/hobby of mine. 

​I have been making videos for 8 years since January 9, 2011 and love every bit of creating them.
I love that you can upload anything to YouTube, and get noticed in some way. YouTube is amazing! 

Over the years, I have mastered multiple video editing programs to create my videos. First program being 'Splice Video Editor'. I then moved on to a very similar editor called 'Perfect Video Editor' which let me do a tiny bit more with my video projects. I then moved onto iMovie back in October 2015 which let me make cuts and do various other details to my videos.

​I plan to start using a much bigger program such as Final Cut Pro X or Adobe Premier in the future! 

Enjoy my channel!

description: I am Alexis Cabanlit and I started learning DSLR and cinematography in 2012. I love film-making to the core. In my first 2 years I spent countless hours just honing my cinematography skills, shooting anything under the sun and making montage films out of it. I love how raw video footages, when perfectly cut and edited in the post, with the accompaniment of the right music, would bring such a powerful visual story of whatever message you want to convey your audience. I have experienced shooting short films, documentaries, prenups, birthday parties and many more. Very recently, I decided to form my own production and this is why this Youtube Channel has come to life -- COLORGRADE FILMS -- the name of my studio. I will be showcasing my sample works here, e.g., short films, documentaries, video reviews and many more to introduce my video productions. If you like my videos, please subscribe and if you want me to cover your event, please message me at colorgradefilms@gmail.com.
